aidoc:AIActivity skos:broadMatch prov:Activity .

aidoc:AIAgent skos:broadMatch prov:Agent .

aidoc:SoftwareComponent skos:narrowMatch prov:SoftwareAgent .

align:55782cad-8f0a-4ee9-b7c4-03931a42e517 a prov:Activity ;
